        "subject": "LU-16035 kfilnd: Set target RX based on local CPT",
        "message": "LU-16035 kfilnd: Set target RX based on local CPT\n\nLNet maps target LNet NIDs to specific CPTs. By telling target LNet\npeers to use the kfilnd RX context associated with that CPT, small\ntransfer size LST RPCs/s significantly increase.\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial\nHPE-bug-id: LUS-10133\nSigned-off-by: Ian Ziemba <ian.ziemba@hpe.com>\nChange-Id: I1317bfd7948f9d0bbe237dbf6a6df0596eee4533\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
